      • get

        WireConnection get(java.lang.String id)
        Gets a wire connection by its identifier, as provided by net.consensys.cava.rlpx.wire.WireConnection#id

      • asIterable

        java.lang.Iterable<WireConnection> asIterable()
        Provides a view of the wire connections as an iterable. There is no guarantee of sorting wire connections.
        Returns:
        an Iterable object allowing to traverse all wire connections held by this repository

      • close

        void close()
        Closes the repository. After it has been closed, the repository should no longer be able to add or retrieve connections.
